{"tid":396742,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"九年感情 輸比三個月😞","createTime":"2017-09-12T02:01:02.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-13T17:39:36.000Z","uid":112041,"like":1,"dislike":253,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1ce288cf8c6a1dabc95753cff5610e3922bd9e57","tid":396742,"uid":112041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T02:01:02.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">首貼別插</span></span><br />\n拍拖九年結婚半年就出去溝仔<br />\n<br />\n比我查到仲話好朋友黎 發埋自己啲相 合成相比佢 都話好朋友？<br />\n<br />\n好啦 原諒你 叫你同男仔講你有老公吾可以再一齊 以為完左件事 點知你又同我講後日同繼續同男仔出街<br />\n<br />\n好我都比你  點知再睇埋你記錄 原來你上埋佢屋企 仲比我知道你自動送上門的 😞<br />\n<br />\n問你點解要甘做 <br />\n係咪我做錯左<br />\n我改啦好冇<br />\n<br />\n你又答吾知  全部都甘答 其實你想點 <br />\n<br />\n跟住我求左你幾日 講個情況比你聽 男仔根本吾鐘意你 會冇將來 <br />\n<br />\n結果求左幾日後 更關手機 已讀不回 <br />\n<br />\n我做錯什麼<br />\n我仲有冇得令佢返轉頭？"},{"pid":"d9946255f73529220d9148ce80dcad41f141682d","tid":396742,"uid":20379,"like":34,"dislike":0,"score":34,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T02:02:30.000Z","msg":"吾你老母"},{"pid":"1fb7ac94ee12cd6c58ec9fbc7e7aabbe470d1123","tid":396742,"uid":20379,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T02:02:46.000Z","msg":"甘你老母"},{"pid":"8757f0e12c16f161d84ccd6183c03e4bcb590654","tid":396742,"uid":9286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T02:02:59.000Z","msg":"半年前應該分手 而唔係結婚"},{"pid":"fa05a0f80f76df4c3288b758ad506c39f42b0ed5","tid":396742,"uid":20379,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T02:03:23.000Z","msg":"轉你老母個老母母母母母"},{"pid":"8e7c85facd2448f0c77372c1b29e8ed3ca29d142","tid":396742,"uid":2419,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T02:03:43.000Z","msg":"雞"},{"pid":"68fa9d68dbddd5dbe2d29e8f22ad7b9a0cb37b2a","tid":396742,"uid":36087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T02:03:44.000Z","msg":"做乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b653143f800b1d5a1f34e56ea6ba6af6c3a3838"